In the distance Lunarpine can see the Maximal base, in the sky he can 
see Falcore. Again the wolf gets on the comm.

"Lunarpine to the flyer above Maximal base, do you read me? We have a 
situation here, Shadow Wing has wandered off and I could use a good 
pair of eyes to help find her."

Though he hadn't been introduced, Falcore was a fellow Maximal, 
hopefully he'd help out.
